<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Активация ваучера</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-100 min-h-screen text-slate-800">
  <%- include('../../partials/vendor-navbar', { user, active: 'activate' }) %>

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24 pb-16 space-y-8">
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
      <header class="space-y-3">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-600">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>
          Активация ваучера клиента
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Введите или отсканируйте код</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Ваучеры статуса <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1">sold</code> или <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1">pending</code> доступны для активации. После успешного ввода статус станет <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1">activated</code>.</p>
      </header>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red-600 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.732-.833-2.5 0L4.314 15.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z" />
            </svg>
            <span><%= error %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-green-200 bg-green-50 px-4 py-4 text-sm text-green-700 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-800">Ваучер активирован</h2>
          <div class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-green-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">
            <p><span class="text-slate-400">Товар:</span> <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900"><%= success.productName %></span></p>
            <p class="mt-2"><span class="text-slate-400">Ключ для клиента:</span> <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono text-slate-700"><%= success.activationKey %></code></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/vendor/activate" class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label for="code" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Код или ключ ваучера</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="code"
            name="code"
            value="<%= form?.code ?? '' %>"
            required
            placeholder="Например, ABCD-1234-EFGH"
            class="mt-2 w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base font-mono tracking-wide text-slate-800 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-200"
          />
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-400">Вы можете отсканировать QR в приложении клиента или ввести код вручную.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
          <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
            Активировать ваучер
          </button>
          <a href="/client/qr-scanner" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition hover:border-indigo-300 hover:text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v1h4V4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1v4h1a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1h-4v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h1v-4H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z" />
            </svg>
            Открыть сканер QR
          </a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
